参考，以下是每个字母（大写或小写）开头的标记数量：</p><pre> <code>{&#39;A&#39;: 4085, &#39;B&#39;: 2243, &#39;C&#39;: 4000, &#39;D&#39;: 2340, &#39;E&#39;: 2371, &#39;F&#39;: 1838, &#39;G&#39;: 1334, &#39;H&#39;: 1531, &#39;I&#39;: 2929, &#39;J&#39;: 492, &#39;K&#39;: 555, &#39;L&#39;: 1612, &#39;M&#39;: 2294, &#39;N&#39;: 1032, &#39;O&#39;: 1935, &#39;P&#39;: 3162, &#39;Q&#39;: 200, &#39;R&#39;: 2794, &#39;S&#39;: 4266, &#39;T&#39;: 2126, &#39;U&#39;: 1293, &#39;V&#39;: 824, &#39;W&#39;: 1165, &#39;X&#39;: 78, &#39;Y&#39;: 252, &#39;Z&#39;: 142}</code></pre><p><br> GPT-J 令牌嵌入作为模糊超球面壳分布在 4096 维空间中，其中心（平均嵌入或“质心”）与原点的欧几里德距离为 1.7158，绝大多数嵌入与此具有欧几里德距离质心大约在 0.9 到 1.1 之间。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:83.64%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rsi9wodhb9gkibro7wbv" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rzd9b3ccl0w18azvnbc8 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/nsktjvpvpffoajbngyzd 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/berczg31st9xsnb5k2bb 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ncejy3hzesatp2zkvudu 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yf5mio26u2oej8zclb5p 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/gmgoukhuylfuj0obgvga 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ww0acv715mom9cvke1fe 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/qz2p3ilq8zqabldug0vm 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/brltpcmkyjzrptmlp8ca 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/itzlrsts7gfkeoxjhmvp 989w"><figcaption> 50257 个 GPT-J 代币到质心的平均距离为 1.0028，最小值和最大值分别为 0.0617 和 1.3086。</figcaption></figure><p>在这个超球形外壳内，我们可以想象与给定探测向量/方向具有最高余弦相似度的标记嵌入簇。因此，例如，“K”的首字母探测向量/方向是由属于以“k”或“K”开头的标记的数百个嵌入“余弦包围”的（忽略前导空格）。</p><p>重复选择一个标记，然后根据其嵌入的余弦相似度对首字母探针进行排序（如下条形图所示），我们看到排名靠前的首字母探针几乎总是与标记的第一个字母匹配，而令牌的后续字母通常在其他排名靠前的首字母探针中大量出现。此外，对于大多数标记，最大的余弦相似度是 26 中唯一的正值。正值和负值通常可以忽略不计，这表明标记嵌入往往会<i>稍微指向</i>相关首字母的方向探测向量，并且<i>与所有其他向量的距离非常小</i>（可能有一两个例外）。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/cemosfl3wpcqqazse2te" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/qcbajgsnzawpmfmeicla 90w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/gppfxhn4h3um7tuxqp5e 180w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/auvacdirygmhmfd3krkj 270w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/aijn9dkk7nytnjdlv2kw 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/k9xcqzkisw0cqd5cf7er 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/d8s1ayhuak8zlfaiwuud 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xv5jsqz7clqwyie3otqr 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/cplkyeg9d4k5b1mxsfan 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/uxlkiiumwhwnew7srdoh 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/