g-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/mrsuk79hqrbc60tnbok4 270w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ghffkvhjhif4kr5zfj1o 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ulpxmpwx4iu2jkuos5lu 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yvord0ypuoiuukcigxky 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/atc8bkrnocn7anj6ycr5 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/wq2lpfonkjcl58y5dbko 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rdiecj15lhk4bnmt1oy8 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ljsaikkn2ndrhujg9iob 866w"><br><br>首字母预测任务：比较基于探测和提示的结果</h2><p>在首字母预测任务中，基于探测的方法（选择 26 个余弦相似度中最大的一个）被发现略优于基于提示的方法。后者涉及零温度提示 GPT-J，模板如下：</p><pre> <code>The string &quot; heaven&quot; begins with the letter &quot;H&quot; The string &quot; same&quot; begins with the letter &quot;S&quot; The string &quot;&lt;token>;&quot; begins with the letter &quot;</code></pre><p>这会输出约 96.7% 的标记的正确字母，而基于探针的方法可实现约 98.7% 的准确度。 <span class="footnote-reference" role="doc-noteref" id="fnrefjbpnruaoncd"><sup><a href="#fnjbpnruaoncd">[5]</a></sup></span>从这个混淆矩阵可以看出，基于提示和基于探测的故障之间的重叠相当小： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:41.48%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/fnxzpnm6jqt1zwqwj78z" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xz0l2xfatzyvttpo0yx7 86w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/r1bevyak8e75aayblgte 166w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/y9i4h7izhvhuk6hbrvdj 246w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/wgc9bnbkgbkcdpxn4b2g 326w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xhiupdlsjn53oxnmlzbo 406w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/kjuhhavlepx4fsyemw3p 486w"></figure><p>不管怎样，两种方法准确性的相似性只能增加人们的怀疑，即<strong>GPT-J 成功完成基于提示的任务的能力在某种程度上取决于其对首字母探测方向的利用</strong>。毕竟，通过访问 26 个方向，实现 GPT-J 的预测准确性水平所需的只是获取点积和比较数量的能力。</p><h2>机制推测</h2><p>迄今为止进行的大量实验表明，可以训练线性探针（取得了不同程度的成功）根据字母存在、第一个字母、第二个字母、第三个字母等、前两个字母、前三个字母、字母数量对标记进行分类、不同字母的数量、大小写、前导空格的存在以及几乎任何其他可以描述的字符级属性。查看与这些学习的探针向量/方向具有最大余弦相似度的标记嵌入列表，我们发现集群显示了所讨论的探针经过训练以区分的属性（数百或数千个带有前导空格的标记，或以“ch”开头，或以“ing”结尾，或包含“j”，或以大写字母开头）。<strong>对这些探测方向的适当库的访问可以轻松地构成能够以 GPT-J 输出中看到的那种准确性进行拼写的算法的基础。</strong></p><p>看看大量 GPT-3“拼写树”可视化（例如上面的“现代”可视化），人们也许可以感觉到这可能是一种模糊的统计算法。未来的工作有望探索<i>基于音素的</i>探测方向存在的可能性。如果确实如此，它们在 GPT 拼写算法中的使用可能会解释<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/5sNLX2yY5FzkCp7Ju/the-spelling-miracle-gpt-3-spelling-abilities-and-glitch#phonetically_plausible">GPT-3 的受限拼写输出中常见的<i>语音正确</i>拼写错误</a>（例如，此处的“INDEAD”、“MOHAMED”、“NICKSON”、“ALINE”） ： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ktbkynqhu71ihpzirbpa" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/zfyqco4s16cpn4wroydo 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/fbaoiljdq8kepstfe6aa 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/oupugwjeqaza4ynprwpj 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ztywemxhuub3q4a3nl7z 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ho00rnfyn00bndotykyj 750w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/lsjshpuv5d8abtd3777w 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/xfhqir6dy1ne9i0lc18g 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/t2iuyx9j3k8zzngotuum 1200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/s2hftaanrguexd8kxcvm 1350w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/yfjpv1n4wjuuzbnolexf 1480w"></figure><p><br>当然，即使事实证明这些线性探测方向如假设的那样<i>被</i>利用，这也不能解释“拼写奇迹”，而是根据一个非常广泛的问题重新表述它“<i>通过什么机制在训练中标记嵌入是否在嵌入空间中以几何方式排列，以便这种基于探针的推理成为可能？</i> ”</p><p></p><h1>通过“减去探测方向”来删除字符级信息</h1><p>为了探索如上所述的线性探测方向与 GPT-J 拼写能力有关的可能性，尝试通过将给定的嵌入向量分解为与相关向量平行和正交的分量来从标记嵌入中删除“首字母信息”。第一个字母探针，然后减去平行分量。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:69.85%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/hlbbvyo6mgvowlqrey2m"><figcaption> <strong>emb = emb_par + emb_perp</strong><br> <strong>emb_perp</strong>位于<strong>探针</strong>的正交互补中</figcaption></figure><p>请注意，通过这样做，我们将<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{emb}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>向量<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{probe}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">正交</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">投影</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">到</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">探针</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">向量</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的正交补集，即由与探针向量正交的所有嵌入向量组成的超平面/子空间。</p><p>这组 50257 个标记被过滤掉了不完全由英语字母表中的大写或小写字母（以及可能的前导空格）组成的任何内容，留下了 46893 个“全罗马”标记，下文将这样称呼它们。对于超过 1000 个随机采样的全罗马标记，对它们的嵌入<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{emb}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>执行正交投影， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{emb\_perp}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">并将</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">结果</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_per</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">插入</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>到以下提示模板中：</p><pre> <code>The string &quot; heaven&quot; begins with the letter &quot;H&quot; The string &quot; same&quot; begins with the letter &quot;S&quot; The string &quot;&lt;emb_perp>;&quot; begins with the letter &quot;</code></pre><p>作为一个具体示例，将标记“peace”的嵌入向量分解为与“P”首字母探测向量<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{w_P}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">P</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>平行和垂直的向量之和，然后减去平行分量。由此产生的嵌入与探测向量的点积必然为零，即<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{w_P}\cdot\mathbf{emb\_perp} = 0."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">P</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">per</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">p</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>所有 26 个经过训练的首字母线性探针都有负偏差。这可能是由于数据不平衡造成的（如果我们查看最大的“首字母”类，则有 4266 个以“S”或“s”开头的标记，以及 42627 个<i>不</i>以“S”或“s”开头的标记，比例为 10:1）。无论如何，这意味着针对给定第一个字母学习的分类器会将适当投影的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb\_perp}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">per p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">p</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>分类为不以该字母开头<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{w}\cdot\mathbf{emb\_perp} + b = b < 0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">，</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">因为</span></span><span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">per</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">p</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{w}\cdot\mathbf{x} + b"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的符号决定了嵌入<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{x}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的分类。</p><h2>预测：首字母信息仍然大量存在</h2><p>也许令人惊讶的是，对于约 94.5% 的标记，GPT-J 在对其嵌入进行正交投影后仍然能够预测正确的第一个字母。不过，令人鼓舞的是，对于它预测错误第一个字母的约 5.5% 的标记中的一半，错误的预测与标记的第二个字母相匹配。</p><p>这表明 GPT-J 的首字母<i>预测算法以某种方式利用了首字母探测方向</i><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{w}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，但在其训练中学习到的相关<i>分类器</i>- 嵌入<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bf{x}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>被积极分类为以相关字母 iff <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{x}\cdot\mathbf{w} + b > 0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">x</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>开头的分类器<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{x}\cdot\mathbf{w} + b > 0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> – 不是，否则这些正交投影嵌入的 100% 将被预测为不以字母开头，而不仅仅是 5.5%。</p><p>那么，GPT-J 是否使用了类似于前面介绍的简单的“最相似余弦探测”方法？回想一下上面的内容，通过识别 26 个首字母探针向量中的哪一个与 token 嵌入具有最大的余弦相似度，可以以大约 98.7% 的准确度来预测随机采样的 token 的第一个字母。</p><p>对整套全罗马标记进行的简单实验支持了这一推测。将嵌入<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b 的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>标记正交投影到<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb\_perp}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_per</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">使用</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">与</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>标记的第一个字母相关的探测方向）后，在 74.4% 的情况下，与<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb\_perp}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>具有最大余弦相似度的第一个字母探测<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb\_perp}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">per</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">仍然</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">是</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>与标记的第一个字母匹配的那个。这些是像“Meg”这样的标记，其中“正确的”首字母探针（此处为“M”）是唯一与嵌入具有正余弦相似度的标记，因此即使通过正交投影减少到零，它仍然存在26 个值中最大的一个： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/w285xibwwdmq7wwwcpbc" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/gedmjo4oyhdj6faqycp9 90w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/lbkrellcjelnpcyyczvf 180w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/a41dsqvs6hlxqan4mnsu 270w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/w4ypqjzbuoam29gt2w1p 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/x8xrrh3nizgrzpymna5l 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ledpdhtsmn1n90mphx8p 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/pdfpzvdwz7cp3l9odvty 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ivgjex9s2ijxzpuwrmzn 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/cok7gdigj75nm781lxfs 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/m1wfepexczh158dun1at 866w"></figure><p>但对于剩下的 25.6%，“最相似余弦探测”方法在正交投影后预测出不正确的第一个字母，我们可以检查错误模式： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/tyjzjxpzqnlhc55zol5l" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/w6ujlbyscgps94kcqj3x 90w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/jvnlbsjl