upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/prvs4ghwpmftmxjxtgqr 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ebmfspdn4m2xkmwm34gd 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/ecc3tpd5l5urrjurymqr 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/e5rkvcsz7rshp8rzoup3 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/cop35xvxrpt632y5csoa 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/vsjzdqvajjvgq2jywvha 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/a07ae8amz547wsh2kuft 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GyaDCzsyQgc48j8t3/rczogpswhs14j1w1wloj 989w"><figcaption> 46893 个全罗马标记中的 45748 个在应用几何反射运算和“最余弦相似探测”方法后产生了错误的首字母预测。</figcaption></figure><p>通过“最相似余弦探测”方法预测无关字母的概率现在已从 34%（正交投影）上升到 44%，但剩余的概率质量根据类似的分布在字母位置上。衰减率。<br></p><h2>反推：首字母信息可靠地消失</h2><p>自然的下一步是将<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb} - 2 * \mathbf{emb\_par}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">∗</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">a</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">r</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>中的因子 2 替换为任意缩放因子<i>k</i> ，以便<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbf{emb} - k * \mathbf{emb\_par}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">e</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">m</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-B" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">b</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-mai